      <title>伊朗袭击测试了美国支持的以色列防空系统的极限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/iran-attack-to-test-limits-of-us-backed-israeli-air-defenses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[早期迹象表明，以色列引以为豪的防空系统通过了迄今为止最大的考验，击退了伊朗前所未有的猛攻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/iran-attack-to-test-limits-of-us-backed-israeli-air-defenses</guid>
